EI.reasoning: Your energy tends to flow inward, gathering strength from depth. Key signals: Moon in Earth (inward-moving); Saturn in Air (outward structure). Note: You may appear more outgoing to others (Ascendant in Water (I-like mask); Sun in Fire (E-like expression); Mars in Fire (E-like ignition)), but this is your interface, not your engine.
EI.falsifiability: If you consistently find that contact energizes you more than solitude and depth, this read would need revision.

NS.reasoning: You tend to read the reality before the theory. Key signals: Sun in Fire (pattern-seeking); Mercury in Water (practical).
NS.falsifiability: This is a close read. If you consistently read meaning and pattern before tangible detail, this read would need revision.

TF.reasoning: You tend to weigh decisions through logic, consistency, and structure. Key signals: Moon in Earth (logic-led); Saturn in Air (structural weight); MC in Fire (value-driven purpose). Note: You may sound more feeling-oriented in conversation (Mercury in Water (empathic speech)), but this is your communication style, not your decision anchor.
TF.falsifiability: If high-stakes decisions consistently feel right through relational coherence rather than structural clarity, this read would need revision.

JP.reasoning: You tend to prefer a settled path and clear closure. Key signals: Sun in Fixed (Blueprint J); Moon in Fixed (closure-seeking tone); Saturn in Mutable (flexible).
JP.falsifiability: If you consistently feel more at ease with options open than with things decided, this read would need revision.
